This fitness tracker was easy to set up, looks great and has standard features like time, steps count, activity levels, calories burned, heartbeat, sleep monitor. The tracker connected easily to my phone and love the blue color. With the choices of color, it can be matching with your outfit easily. I compared between my phone and was happy to see an accurate step count. It also displays messages, incoming calls and charging is also convenient. This activity watch is stylish, functional, fashionable and meets my needs perfectly! 
